metadata.name: Custom Stage API (AFTERBIRTH+ ONLY)
metadata.description:
Afterbirth+ version of StageAPI. Out of date and unsupported, but should function with old mods.
The Repentance and only supported version of Custom Stage API can be found [url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1348031964]here[/url].
